        "rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "🔧 1. Model Context Protocol (MCP)"}}]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "heading_3",
      "heading_3": {
        "rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "简介"}}]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "paragraph": {
        "rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "Model Context Protocol（MCP）是由 Anthropic 在 2024 年 11 月发布的开放标准协议，旨在解决 AI 应用与外部数据源和工具之间的集成问题。到 2026 年，MCP 已经成为 AI 工具生态系统的\"通用接口\"。"}}]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "heading_3",
      "heading_3": {
        "rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "为什么值得关注"}}]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "paragraph": {
        "rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "技术价值："}}]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "bulleted_list_item",
      "bulleted_list_item": {
        "rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "标准化集成：提供统一的协议让 LLM 应用连接数据库、文件系统、API 等外部资源"}}]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "bulleted_list_item",
      "bulleted_list_item": {
        "rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "减少重复工作：一次集成，处处可用（One standard. One integration. Works everywhere）"}}]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "bulleted_list_item",
      "bulleted_list_item": {
        "rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "降低维护成本：避免 N×M 的连接器混乱局面"}}]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "paragraph": {
        "rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "应用场景："}}]
      }
    },
